title: #526 - Felicia Michaels
description:
Felicia Michaels, Comedian and director of the film, "Pervs" featuring past guests Susanna Lee, Felipe Esparza, and Sam Tripoli, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt in studio.

"Pervs" will be a part of the LA Femme Film Festival on October 20th. LAfemme.org
